                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm lucky in that I have  a regular exp group but while they don't forbid me to use charm, they'd far prefer that  I didn't and I have to say, I agree with them.
<br />

<br />
We can kill far more quickly without a charm'ed pet AND we avoid all of the risk associated with a pet. (Risk: wipe or cleric dieing, no evac'er , no easy means of cr if in a non pop zone).  
<br />

<br />
So although I can see how this is a big nerf to enchanter's that charm solo, personally for me its not a big deal. 
<br />

<br />
