I realized how bored I was when I started reading message boards in groups.
<br />

<br />
There was nothing to do.  Adds didn't come.  I hit my nuke key every 6 seconds.  Wait for proc/incite message, tash, slow, hit nuke key, tab off to read another sentance, tab back and hit nuke key.
<br />

<br />
Rebuff when someone dies.
<br />

<br />
Zzzzzzz.
<br />

<br />
I'd say I cancelled my account over this, but I (try to) cancel it every month just in case I don't decide to log in for a few days between subscriptions.  The questions is will I bother logging in again?
<br />

<br />
There is an item I wouldn't mind having (outside of EQ-utility, the concept of it is interesting to me), so I might log in the next time my guild hits that target.  But I haven't had fun in OoW zones yet.  Possibly part of it is my recent lag problems, /shrug.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by Yakk on Thu Sep 23, 2004 4:36 pm; edited 1 time in total</span></td>
